ToolStripControlHost.Dispose(false) runs from Component.Finalize().  It must
not dispose the hosted Control from that finalizer path: disposing WinForms
controls can remove them from parent collections and trigger managed layout,
including TextRenderer.MeasureText, on the finalizer thread while controls and
fonts are already in teardown.  Only the explicit Dispose(true) path should
dispose the hosted managed control.

